description:
This dataset is underlying the scientific publication titled "Naked-Eye Molecular Testing for the Detection of Xylella fastidiosa in Mallorca (Balearic Island) Almond Orchards by Colorimetric LAMP", published in the&nbsp; Applied Sciences &nbsp;journal.&nbsp; 
 The dataset includes results of qPCR detection of  Xylella fastidiosa  Xfm in samples collected on Summer 2023 from two experimental orchards located in Mallorca Island, Spain.  The provided information in the dataset are further discussed and interpreted in detail, as well as their subsequent results,&nbsp;in the scientific publication. 
 This research was conducted through a joint action of the EU&rsquo;s Horizon 2020 Projects No. 887281 &lsquo;Biovexo; Biocontrol of Xylella and its vector in olive trees for integrated pest management&rsquo; (GA n. 887281), &lsquo;FREE@POC; Towards an instrument-FREE future of molecular diagnostics at the Point-Of-Care&rsquo; (GA n. 862840) and also partially supported by &lsquo;BEXYL&rsquo; (Beyond Xylella, Integrated Management Strategies for Mitigating Xylella fastidiosa impact in Europe; grant number 101060593).

